articles.title: Israel signals readiness for new temporary truce in Gaza as pressure mounts - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Hamas says it will not enter negotations over releasing captives until Israel ends its war on Gaza.
articles.content:
Israeli President Isaac Herzog has said his country is willing to agree a new temporary truce with Hamas in Gaza to secure the release of more captives held by the Palestinian group.
